text: Convenient and even has PayNow option. However, clothes do not smell clean after washing and drying, even after choosing ozone and softener options.

My items got stolen. Asked for cctv footage, they say only police can view. I made police report, and their cctv conveniently not working that day. Police mentioned that they always received reports about them and always cctv not working that day. Very shady, might be an inside job.

Visit the other laundromat instead, the shoe shop uncle beside is the boss. If anything u can ask him to view cctv, he very nice
